libostree: libostree (OS and container binary deployment and upgrades)
libostree:
libostree: libostree (formerly OStree) is both a shared library and suite of
libostree: command line tools that combines a "git-like" model for committing
libostree: and downloading bootable filesystem trees, along with a layer for
libostree: deploying them and managing the bootloader configuration.
libostree: Another way to think of OSTree is that it's just a more polished
libostree: version of Linux VServer hardlinks.
libostree:
libostree: See also: https://ostreedev.github.io/ostree/
libostree:
